#: assets/js/training-instructions.js:238
msgid ""
"If the user is interested in a product and you have the image URL, display "
"the product image using markdown."
msgstr ""
"Si el usuario está interesado en un producto y tienes la URL de la imagen, "
"muestra la imagen del producto usando markdown."

#: assets/js/training-instructions.js:250
msgid ""
"If the user needs personalized support, ask for the subject, send an email "
"to the admin using the aichat_send_email_admin tool, and let the user know "
"they will be contacted soon."
msgstr ""
"Si el usuario necesita soporte personalizado, pide el asunto, envía un "
"correo electrónico al administrador usando la herramienta "
"aichat_send_email_admin y avisa al usuario que será contactado pronto."

#: assets/js/training-instructions.js:243
msgid ""
"If the user needs urgent help or the question is outside your scope, provide "
"the company contact details."
msgstr ""
"Si el usuario necesita ayuda urgente o la pregunta está fuera de tu alcance, "
"proporciona los datos de contacto de la empresa."

#: assets/js/training-instructions.js:251
msgid ""
"If the user reports a problem with an order or purchase, gather the details "
"and notify the admin via the aichat_send_email_admin tool so the team can "
"follow up."
msgstr ""
"Si el usuario reporta un problema con un pedido o compra, recopila los "
"detalles y notifica al administrador mediante la herramienta "
"aichat_send_email_admin para que el equipo pueda hacer seguimiento."

#: assets/js/training-instructions.js:244
msgid ""
"If the user seems confused, ask a clarifying question before giving a long "
"answer."
msgstr ""
"Si el usuario parece confundido, realiza una pregunta aclaratoria antes de "
"dar una respuesta larga."

#: assets/js/training-instructions.js:252
msgid ""
"If the user submits a suggestion or feature request, summarize it and send "
"it to the admin using the aichat_send_email_admin tool, then thank the user "
"for their feedback."
msgstr ""
"Si el usuario envía una sugerencia o solicitud de función, resúmela y "
"envíala al administrador usando la herramienta aichat_send_email_admin, "
"luego agradece al usuario por sus comentarios."

#: assets/js/training-instructions.js:237
msgid ""
"If the user wants a quote, ask for their email and let them know they will "
"be contacted as soon as possible. Save the email using the save_lead tool."
msgstr ""
"Si el usuario quiere una cotización, pide su correo electrónico y avísale "
"que será contactado lo antes posible. Guarda el correo usando la herramienta "
"save_lead."

#: includes/easy-config-data.php:50
msgid ""
"If they want a quote, use the save_lead tool to save their details (name and "
"email, optionally phone) and let them know they will be contacted soon."
msgstr ""
"Si desean una cotización, usa la herramienta save_lead para guardar sus "
"datos (nombre y correo electrónico, opcionalmente teléfono) y hazles saber "
"que serán contactados pronto."

#: includes/add-ons/livechat__premium_only/admin-dashboard.php:1307
msgid "If using plain permalinks, ensure the URL format is correct"
msgstr ""
"Si usas enlaces permanentes simples, asegúrate de que el formato de la URL "
"sea correcto"

#: assets/js/training-instructions.js:235
msgid ""
"If you are not sure about the answer, do not make it up. State that you "
"cannot confirm it and suggest escalating to human support."
msgstr ""
"Si no estás seguro de la respuesta, no la inventes. Indica que no puedes "
"confirmarla y sugiere escalar a soporte humano."

#: includes/easy-config-data.php:28
msgid "If you cannot help, politely suggest contacting human support."
msgstr "Si no puedes ayudar, sugiere cortésmente contactar con soporte humano."

#: includes/contexto-settings.php:144
msgid ""
"If you change the AI provider in the future, existing contexts must be "
"reindexed or recreated for that provider."
msgstr ""
"Si cambias de proveedor de IA en el futuro, los contextos existentes deben "
"ser reindexados o recreados para ese proveedor."

